data.description: Welcome to 45023 Sancroft Ave, a 4 bedroom and 2.5 bathroom beautiful pool home located in the heart of Lancaster. This lovely home boasts 1,723 square feet of living space on a 6,996 square foot lot with attached 2 car garage. Upon entering, you will be delighted with the spacious and bright living room. Adjacent to the living room is the dining area and kitchen. The kitchen is a chef’s dream with modern appliances, granite countertops, and ample storage and counterspace. The family room has a great view of the backyard and pool, and features a fireplace. The lovely home has 4 spacious bedrooms and 2.5 well-appointed bathrooms for comfort and convenience. Some of the bell and whistles that come with this home include: solar panels, camera security system, new grill, pool heater, recently painted fence, and material to replace the floor of the second level. Centrally located in Lancaster, this home enjoys close proximity to Deputy Pierre W. Bain Park, Eastside Pool, Metrolink, schools, shopping, and dining. Contact us for a showing today!
